         python3-setuptools (>=59.6.0),
         python3-gi (>=3.42.1),
         python3-gi-cairo (>=3.42.1),
Description: Python 3 package for GEOPM service.  Provides the
 implementation for the geopmd service daemon and interfaces for
 configuring the service.
